@startuml
actor User
participant AppLayout
participant BreakpointService
participant NavigationManager

User -> AppLayout : open app
AppLayout -> BreakpointService : read viewport
BreakpointService --> AppLayout : mobile / tablet / desktop
AppLayout -> NavigationManager : render route shell
User -> AppLayout : resize / navigate
AppLayout -> BreakpointService : recalculate
AppLayout --> User : adaptive nav UI
@enduml
